article_title: Memorial Hermann chooses leader for Cypress expansion

article_metadata.description: Memorial Hermann recently purchased 32 acres at U.S. 290 and the Grand Parkway in Cypress where it plans to build a medical center with inpatient  and outpatient services.  "Scott has built a 30-year career in health care," Memorial Hermann's chief operating officer Chuck Stokes said in a written statement.
